			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This item is found on a very rare paladin spawn in Rathe Mountains named Quid Rhilestone (sp?). His spawn spot is random, around the paladin camp. After he sapwns, he walks from the gipsy camp, through the paladin camp, towards the orc camp.<BR>
<BR>
He hits hard (90ies) and uses lots of heals, and the LoH. He is somewhere around 35-40th level.<BR>
<BR>
Fire beetles, bears etc. are belived to be placeholders, so killing them may help to get him to spawn.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
