			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				His name is Quid Rhilstone, he's an erudite paladin, he spawns in the paladin camp area in Rathe Mountains and walks around there.  He is between level 30 and 34, I'd estimate, because he conned blue to a level 35 character.  However, he often doubles, and hits for damage up into the 70s against a 720 AC.  As a paladin, he will lay on hands, and he heals himself when his health gets low (and channels amazingly well).<BR>
<BR>
I expect if he's carrying the Man-O-War, you'd be able to see it, I expect the Siryn Hair Hood is his common drop.
				</font>
			</td>

